{"answer":"Yes. The earliest production lot build_date is earlier than the earliest calibration production_release_date. Earliest production row: lot_id LOT-0001, plant_code BER, line_id L4, shift C, build_date 2021-01-01, release_status HOLD. Earliest calibration row: calibration_id CAL-0001, platform_code PX-11, engine_family I4T, production_release_date 2021-01-15, fuel_map_revision FMR-2.7, ecu_checksum 0xA4C91E2B. Comparison used: build_date 2021-01-01 < production_release_date 2021-01-15."}

